Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在国外有这样的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说通过跟病人说话  使他们苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在昏迷状态下？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概可以传达到深层意识里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是否能理解话语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话语？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川煌那里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一点都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是变得完全写不出文章了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  他有了位很好的担当
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.13,0:03:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏香的姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏香和要  你还记得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都来看望你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文  再一起去学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加文化祭  运动会  还有从未参加过的社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交很多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我早就在想了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初在保健室里和我交谈的是美歌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我在学校…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初我搭话的  的确是文歌没错  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是美川文歌  请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是“我”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}小文自称时用的是“私”（多用于女性自称）\N美歌自称时用的是“仆”（多用于年轻男生自称）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  原来文伽也去了学校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校很好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是帮她制造一个契机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让小文交上朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我喜欢上的  难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽  差不多该走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没那个心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少见  工作热心的文伽小姊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的  有点棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我吗  文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后文是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是死者寄来的这一点我明白  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要符合死后文的规定  什么都可以送到哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  那就是传说中的文伽的本体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就奇怪你怎么能长大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  是因为你并没有死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真苫  你没说出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用文字传达出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\bord0\fs29}没\N说\N出\N去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦  还没告诉别的邮递员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你特地来看我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能  我哪有那么闲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去玩吧  买木天蓼的钱还剩着些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这不是闲得很吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是在看山  这次去看海吧  比如南方的小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也算缘分  你们也一块来吧  现在放暑假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许你很闲  我们接下来可要去工作  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还挺通情达理的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换  由我来决定地点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到真的是南方的小岛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是国内的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不飞过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓旅行  是指连路途也要好好享受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是搞不懂人类
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能明白  移动很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移动…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没错咧  因为我会变成人类的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦是会应验的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  千章也是邮递员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是死人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是交通事故啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和对面行驶来的车  嘭地撞个正着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短暂的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你开车技术超烂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笨啊  开车这种事是交给男人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于男人和女人的事  什么都可以请教姊姊我哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是站在夕阳下  大喊了“我喜欢文歌”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底怎么跟她说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你住嘴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的房间？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  这是你第一次住民宿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第一次…旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那么  我们来指教你享受旅行的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔枕头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我也想扔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我来倒茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必客气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水天宫岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在那里是无人岛  什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁边的岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌说目的地不是这  是旁边的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁边的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌到底在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易和文歌再会了  不告白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时只是吓了一跳  并不是因为讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家都那么说了  你就再告白一次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是初中时的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:08:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在都过了时效了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱是无所谓时效的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是喜欢她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和夏香你无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为文歌是我的朋友  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把通讯功能用于偷听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么啊  你明明是当事人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被告白了对吧  那个眼镜男
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么想的  或是有了其他喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死人还是活人?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你自己吧  而且是女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很明白  什么是喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  你一直和父亲相依为命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千章呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千章有过很多次…恋爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛…算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是陈年往事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  美川煌老师的原稿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗  亏你能拿到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了  我是预定了房间的白河
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么陪我来南方的小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是有工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  那座岛上有死后文的收信人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:10:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是刚才问过阿姨  说那是无人岛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  文伽  有谁在那岛上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指邮递员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  说不定只是具尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弃尸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再讲啦  这之后可是要去那个岛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者很老实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  活着的人才比较可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是犯人在怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定刚杀掉  正把凶器埋进洞里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说得很有趣似的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  文歌  不要开这种奇怪的玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏香  不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  你要不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶…器

Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  吓到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是去扫墓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那镰刀是用来除草的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扫墓？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真佩服  这么年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都五年没去扫墓了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实有个中意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想对他告白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不知是没有勇气  或是害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时电视上恋爱占卜说  恋爱的lucky chance是扫墓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  你也是单相思组员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除我之外  大家都在单相思中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗   我对小文
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难受吧  告白就像dead or alive吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走上这条路  最后是生还是死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能理解我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱或许可以成真
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要是失败了  连朋友也做不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好  青春～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千章没有这种经历吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊  基本上属于经常被人家告白的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个没品的男生告白说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“千章  我希望成为你的避雷之所”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他大概是想说“避雷针”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常应该说是“想成为守护你的盾”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也很没品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千章  你在倒什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是未成年人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是未成年人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少来了  恋爱的事不借点酒意怎么说得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢那个眼镜男吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡什么觉啊  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满身酒味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我你喜欢的人吧  这可是旅行的乐趣所在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那么按顺时针顺序恋爱特训  夏香第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关掉灯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们一直闹到早上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子们共处的晚上可是很宝贵的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学到不少东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了岛上马上去扫墓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是可以的话  和我们一起游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  扫完墓以后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  等你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.93,0:14:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  是替谁扫墓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爷爷  清澄的家原本在那岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我爷爷的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟我妈妈姓  所以姓氏不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爷爷的  名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄才藏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  你爷爷难道是武士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他结婚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私人沙滩～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果  还是不知道文歌选这座岛的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  能跟仗一起游泳的也就得是在无人岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不游吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了我出生的镇子  时隔多年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…什么都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家  学校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的商店  经常玩耍的公园
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后都过了五十年了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有变化的只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母  朋友  大家都去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋人也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过之后他也活了五十年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前说过的因为猫和他相遇的那人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点羡慕能长大的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千章  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.54,0:17:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扫墓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  这可不是食物哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也能来上坟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷  这两位是文歌和千章
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这的途中交上的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄才藏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的一生幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:17:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚  有了可爱的孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定很幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最后的愿望也是  希望才藏能在我死后一直活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄信人是清澄才藏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  你的工作是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人  会是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷明明一直独身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈是养女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候因为交通事故失去了父母
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被爷爷领养的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  千章
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上周的电影也很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参观美术馆也很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识千章你后  一直很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  从今以后  一直和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个…笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉我  再找一个不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  求婚的话  要有戒指啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用墓碑代替
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子没品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我宣誓…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个轮到我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了就去告白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下定决心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不由得…

Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.69,0:21:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fnDFLiSong-Bd\i1\bord0\fs24}{\fad(1100,1700)}死後文\N\N第九話\N\N再會

Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.00,0:23:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回忆过去的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找未来的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.33,0:23:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人约定的是液状的世界
